OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1776795065
OL,3,CTwo guilty over drive-by shooting
OL,4,Cmurder of mother at wake in Willesden
OL,6,FTwo men have been found guilty of
OL,7,Fmurdering an innocent woman in a drive-
OL,8,Fby shooting outside a wake and
OL,9,Finjuring two more people.
OL,11,FMother-of-two Michelle Sadio, 44, was
OL,12,Fgunned down outside the River of Life
OL,13,FPentecostal Church in Willesden, north
OL,14,FLondon, on December 14 2024.
OL,16,FShe had been among around 100
OL,17,Fmourners, including children as young
OL,18,Fas five, to attend the wake for 80-
OL,19,Fyear-old Dianne Boatong.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
