FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1776795065
OL,3,CTwo guilty over drive-by shooting
OL,4,Cmurder of mother at wake in Willesden
OL,6,FAt around 9pm, guests were outside on
OL,7,Fthe pavement when a black Kia pulled
OL,8,Fup and shots were fired into the crowd.
OL,10,FMs Sadio, a legal administrator, was
OL,11,Fhit and died at the scene.
OL,13,FTransport for London contractor
OL,14,FKenneth Amoah, 39, was hit in the back
OL,15,Fand paralysed below the waist, and
OL,16,Fself-employed Kadeem Francis, 32, was
OL,17,Fshot in the foot.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1776795065
OL,3,CTwo guilty over drive-by shooting
OL,4,Cmurder of mother at wake in Willesden
OL,6,FThe intended target was said to have
OL,7,Fbeen a rapper called Trapstar Toxic,
OL,8,Freal name Adetokunbo Ajibola, 33, who
OL,9,Fwas at the event.
OL,11,FAfter an Old Bailey trial, Perry Allen-
OL,12,FThomas, 27, and Amir Salem, 20, were
OL,13,Ffound guilty of murder and two counts
OL,14,Fof attempted murder.
OL,16,FRapper Shaquille Sutherland, known as
OL,17,FLil Shak, 26, from Wembley, and Tahjin
OL,18,FSommersall, 19, from Feltham, west
OL,19,FLondon, were cleared of wrongdoing.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1776795065
OL,3,CTwo guilty over drive-by shooting
OL,4,Cmurder of mother at wake in Willesden
OL,6,FThe prosecution had alleged Mr
OL,7,FSommersall had been in the Kia with
OL,8,Ftwo other men, who fled the country
OL,9,Fafter the incident.
OL,11,FAt least four shots were fired,
OL,12,Falthough it was not known who in the
OL,13,FKia pulled the trigger.
OL,15,FAllen-Thomas, from Wembley, north
OL,16,FLondon, was said to have helped
OL,17,Forganise the shooting but ensured he
OL,18,Fwas elsewhere at the time.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1776795065
OL,3,CTwo guilty over drive-by shooting
OL,4,Cmurder of mother at wake in Willesden
OL,6,FThe Kia used in the attack had been
OL,7,Fstolen and was being driven with false
OL,8,Fnumber plates.
OL,10,FAfter the shooting, it was doused in
OL,11,Fpetrol and set alight.
OL,13,FSalem, from Wembley, had bought some
OL,14,Fof the petrol used to set the fire,
OL,15,Fjurors heard.
OL,17,FOn the night of the shooting, Salem
OL,18,Fwas in contact with the Kia occupants
OL,19,Fand reported back to Allen-Thomas,
OL,20,Fjurors were told.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1776795065
OL,3,CTwo guilty over drive-by shooting
OL,4,Cmurder of mother at wake in Willesden
OL,6,FThe weapon used in the shooting had
OL,7,Fbeen used twice before in the previous
OL,8,Ffew months, and was said to be a "gang
OL,9,Fgun".
OL,11,FIn one of the earlier incidents, the
OL,12,Foccupant of a car opened fire on a
OL,13,Fgroup of males outside a pizzeria,
OL,14,Fdischarging 11 rounds and hitting one
OL,15,Fperson in the ankle.
OL,17,FThere was no suggestion the defendants
OL,18,Fwere involved.
OL,26,@pD@bOUqD@DO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1776795065
OL,3,CTwo guilty over drive-by shooting
OL,4,Cmurder of mother at wake in Willesden
OL,6,FGiving evidence in his trial, Mr
OL,7,FSommersall denied being in the Kia and
OL,8,Fclaimed to have been on a council
OL,9,Festate in Wembley at the time of the
OL,10,Fshooting.
OL,12,FThe other defendants denied being
OL,13,Finvolved in any way or knowing
OL,14,Fanything about it.
OL,16,FAfter the verdicts on Tuesday, Mrs
OL,17,FJustice McGowan remanded the two
OL,18,Fconvicted defendants into custody to
OL,19,Fbe sentenced at a later date.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/8
